The Alfred (http://www.alfred.org.au/); 
The Northern Hospital (http://www.nh.org.au/ locations/the-northern- 
					hospital); 
The Royal Children's Hospital (http://www.rch.org.au/home/); 
The Royal Victorian Eye and Ear 
					Hospital (http://www.eyeandear.org.au/); 
The Royal Women's Hospital (http://www.thewomens.org.au/); and 
Western Hospital (http://www.westernhealth.org. 
					au/Pages/default.aspx).




					Smart Antenna - Green Solution Investment Tax Credit 




					In conjunction with our reseller, We Build Apps, a Green 
					Solution has been designed to enable our Smart Antenna to 
					run using solar power and with a battery back-up.  
					These added Green Solution refinements, will allow for our 
					Smart Antenna to qualify for the Investment Tax Credit 
					program that is offered by the United States' federal 
					government.  





					ONE OF THE LARGEST INSURANCE COMPANIES IN NORTH AMERICA 
					DEEMED  THE SMART ANTENNA AS A SECURITY DEVICE which will 
					open new markets for Isign AS WELL AS MAJOR DISCOUNTS OFF OF 
					INSURANCE PREMIUMS.




					iSIGN Invited to be an Approved Vendor to the US Military 
					Channel

iSIGN 
					has been selected and is proceeding with the application 
					paperwork with the United States government to enable our 
					Smart Antennas to be installed in PX stores on US military 
					bases throughout the United States and the Middle East to 
					provide messaging on product sales and services to base 
					personnel.  The devices will also provide security 
					protection to the base, as it will on the Crocker Park site 
					installations, as well as the ability for service men and 
					women to become loyalty members and provide a greater 
					security and convenience network on military locations.

iSIGN's network push solutions 
					along with our Smart Antennas recent recognition as a 
					security device led to this invitation.

ISIGN IS THE FIRST CORPORATION TO 
					RECEIVE A PATENT IN THIS GENRE and has filed for OR IS 
					GETTING READY TO FILE  additional patents that could change 
					 THE  landscape of both  APPLE AND GOOGLE.

